description:
On today’s show, Emily is joined by acupuncturist and Master of Chinese Medicine, Christian Cristiano, to talk about energy, acupuncture & how it all can affect your sex life. Plus, she’s answering your emails. 

Emily gives insight on how to take the amazing dynamic you share in the bedroom with your partner and apply it to other parts of the relationship, can the time of day have an effect on different types of orgasms, & what physical vs. romantic attraction means. 

Thank you for supporting our sponsors who help keep the show FREE: Promescent, Away Luggage, SiriusXM, Muse, Veritas Farms. 

Follow Emily on all social: @sexwithemily

For even more sex talk, tips, & tricks visit sexwithemily.com
